      <p></p>
<p>During bereavement, practical support is invaluable. Offer assistance and understanding through these thoughtful messages.</p>
<li>If you need anything at all, please don't hesitate to ask.</li>
<li>We're here to help in any way we can, big or small.</li>
<li>Please let us know if there's anything we can do to ease your burden.</li>
<li>We'd like to help with meals, errands, or anything you might need.</li>
<li>Please accept this small gesture of support during this difficult time.</li>
<li>Thinking of you and offering my support in whatever way you need.</li>
<li>Let us know how we can provide practical assistance.</li>
<li>We're here to lend a hand during this time of sorrow.</li>
<li>We want to help in any way we can. Please let us know.</li>
